**Worker Testimonials:**

*"Before, I would travel 2 hours to collect cash. Now I get money on my phone in minutes."* - Emmanuel, Carpenter

*"I was afraid of crypto, but this was so easy. Now I have a wallet for savings too."* - Amina, Site Manager

