## Choosing the Right Use Case

### Decision Matrix

Use Bridgelet when:

| Criteria | Importance | Threshold |
|----------|------------|-----------|
| Recipients lack wallets | ✅ Critical | > 50% |
| Payment frequency | ✅ Critical | Infrequent or one-time |
| Payment urgency | ⭐ High | Minutes/hours matter |
| Recipient reachability | ⭐ High | SMS/email works |
| Transaction size | ⭐ Medium | > $10 |
| Scale | ⭐ Medium | 100+ recipients |

### Not Ideal For

❌ **Frequent micro-payments to same users**
- Better: Direct wallet payments after first onboarding

❌ **Recipients already have wallets**
- Better: Standard Stellar transactions

❌ **Amounts < $5**
- Reason: Onboarding effort not justified

❌ **No way to reach recipients**
- Requirement: SMS, email, or app notification needed

